{"tid":2364346,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟戰線｜36個國際人權組織去信歐盟 若無有力人權條款 應否決《歐中投資協議》】","createTime":"2021-01-13T02:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T02:36:21.000Z","uid":218158,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4b76d0aeda57bf5856dda90e40b849712bb5bdc8","tid":2364346,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T02:26:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1410156110/276704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1410156110%2F276704&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvERnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=13a027e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1410156110/276704</a><br />\n<br />\n《歐中投資協議》能否獲歐洲議會通過成為今年焦點，有香港手足「港民國際連橫」與30多個全球各地的人權組織共同去信歐洲理事會主席、歐盟執委會主席、歐洲議會主席、人權事務專員及一眾歐洲議員，要求重新考慮是否簽署《協議》。<br />\n<br />\n他們指出，《歐盟條約》第21條要求歐盟在國際上的行為必須尊重人權等原則，與第三國建立合作關係時，亦應訂明共同政策及措施，合力達致民主、法治、人權等原則。<br />\n<br />\n他們批評，《歐中投資協議》不但無視中共人權狀況劣積斑斑，但《協議》亦竟然沒有「人權條款」，做法違反《歐盟條約》的要求。<br />\n<br />\n為此，他們促請歐洲議員，若然《協議》沒有加入強力及可執行的「人權條款」，而中共沒有正式批准《國際勞工組織公約》前，不應通過相關《協議》。<br />\n<br />\n他們同時發起全球聯署，希望更多人可以加入戰線，向歐洲議會施壓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKGlobalConnect/status/1349131534695948290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGlobalConnect%2Fstatus%2F1349131534695948290&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvERnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=b94714b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGlobalConnect%2Fstatus%2F1349131534695948290&h=c61aca27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKGlobalConnect/status/1349131534695948290</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LauraHarth/status/1349128707747815438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLauraHarth%2Fstatus%2F1349128707747815438&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvERnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=62b9a26b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLauraHarth%2Fstatus%2F1349128707747815438&h=5e52fefc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LauraHarth/status/1349128707747815438</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AMFChina/status/1349132383249977349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAMFChina%2Fstatus%2F1349132383249977349&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvERnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=3b2952df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAMFChina%2Fstatus%2F1349132383249977349&h=489a74ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AMFChina/status/1349132383249977349</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署連結<br />\n<a href=\"http://globalcommitteefortheruleoflaw.org/joint-cso-appeal-on-eu-china-cai/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fglobalcommitteefortheruleoflaw.org%2Fjoint-cso-appeal-on-eu-china-cai%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvERnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=cec17486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://globalcommitteefortheruleoflaw.org/joint-cso-appeal-on-eu-china-cai/</a>"},{"pid":"a7263750d9801328233f26ca2c2ecd79adfc8e2d","tid":2364346,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T02:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce78c291e4e36df5ffae954fbdc93f7cccaa41e","tid":2364346,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7263750d9801328233f26ca2c2ecd79adfc8e2d","tid":2364346,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T02:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T02:29:20.000Z","msg":"噉快"},{"pid":"f8f0be03e08a2f7240e8d2e9542f33d5fa6425d8","tid":2364346,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T02:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcb082314